body_html:
@drpngx It doesn't seem like a tf_decorator issue.

Compare
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/v1.1.0-rc2/tensorflow/python/util
and
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/python/util

See that tf_decorator exists in 'master' but not in 1.1.0-rc2. I don't think the decorator work had landed when 1.1.0-rc2 was cut.
